descriptionHtml:
MELP all-in-one Employee App is a tool for personalized engagement, communication, flexible benefits management & beyond.

With the ability to individually choose benefits from an international marketplace and features like a Recognition system or Feedback Inbox, it is a must-have for modern employers striving for improved retention through personalized employee experience.
descriptionShort: Next-level personalised employee benefits and engagement at your fingertips.

With the ability to individually choose benefits from an international marketplace and features like a Recognition system or Feedback Inbox, it is a must-have for modern employers striving for improved retention through personalized employee experience.
descriptionShort: Next-level personalised employee benefits and engagement at your fingertips.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Hi. Have fun exploring yet another new update - this time presenting:
- full image preview in shop item
We are continuously listening to the feedback of our users to improve their experience and roll out new features.
